lead_paragraph: A sweet homecoming was never likely for Brock Osweiler in Denver on Monday but the Houston Texans quarterback got much more than he bargained for as he delivered a nightmare performance against the Broncos in a 27-9 loss.

headline.print_headline: No Sweet Return to Mile High for Fumbling Osweiler
